## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely cause |
| --- | --- |
| Member gets 404 on campaign | `include: { members: true }` missing in service |
| Public character 403 for guest | `visibility !== PUBLIC` in seed |
| ADMIN fails | bypass not first line in policy |
| Tests pass locally, fail CI | truncate order missing new FK table |

